## Project layout

```
src/shellforgepy/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ geometry/        # Pure NumPy/ SciPy helpers
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ construct/       # Alignment and composition primitives
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ produce/         # Arrangement + export helpers
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ adapters/        # Optional cadquery/ and freecad/ backends
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ simple.py        # Convenience facade with auto-selected adapter
```

